Global DMARC Tool Market Insights
DMARC Tool Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 17.5% from 2024 to 2030.

DMARC Tool Market Overview
The DMARC (Domain-based Message Authentication, Reporting & Conformance) tool market is experiencing substantial growth, valued at approximately USD 1.7 billion in 2024. With organizations increasingly prioritizing email security, DMARC tools play a critical role in protecting businesses from phishing attacks, domain spoofing, and email fraud. This market is anticipated to grow at a CAGR of 16.4% from 2024 to 2032, reaching USD 7.1 billion by 2032. This rapid expansion is driven by the surge in cyber threats and the growing need for enterprises to safeguard their communication infrastructure and data privacy.

